black pepper
sake
salt
veg oil
watermellon cubes
arugula
soy sauce
rice wine vinegar
goat cheese

Infuse watermellon chumks in sake for 3 hours. Combine juices, soy sauce, vinegar, oil and emulsify with whisk. Combine fruit, vinegrette, goat cheese, and arugula and lightly toos with fresh ground pepper. Salt to taste.
